00:11:03.240 --> 00:11:06.440
'Sudah berhari-hari sejak
aku melihat Radhika-ku.'

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:07.760
'Yug!'

00:11:11.760 --> 00:11:14.440
'Ajeet, putar mobilnya.
Yug bersama Radha.'

00:11:14.560 --> 00:11:15.960
'Yug masih hidup.'

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:25.000
